[link: /commands/categories/filters.md] ’Щ@38e6fd0295df7b32dd0c6f3127c4f1beeb3bb96d765c7637589d338f0b8a23a2ЩQTitle: title: get
Path: Signature
Content:
``> get {flags} (cell_path) ...rest``
’Щ@9ad2c502ae2303a38b7a5ef6e1a09baf27af2254841a15fd80d4ec898d4e956aЪtTitle: title: get
Path: Flags
Content:
``--optional, -o``
: Make all cell path members optional (returns 
``null``
 for missing values).
``--ignore-case``
: Make all cell path members case insensitive.
``--ignore-errors, -i``
: Ignore missing data (make all cell path members optional) (deprecated).
``--sensitive, -s``
: Get path in a case sensitive manner (deprecated).
’Щ@be34218551bb43e824ecedda28789d1f0525e70b4dd908c572929cef48d80c91Щ|Title: title: get
Path: Parameters
Content:
``cell_path``
: The cell path to the data.
``...rest``
: Additional cell paths.
